OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy for many with drizzle in
OL,6,Fplaces. Heavier and more persistent
OL,7,Frain arriving from the west through
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Turning windier with
OL,9,Fstrong southwesterly winds in coastal
OL,10,Fregions, with gales possible on
OL,11,Fexposed western coasts for a time.
OL,12,FStaying mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FHeavy rain becoming mostly
OL,15,Fconfined to south Wales this evening
OL,16,Fwith lighter, patchier rain lingering
OL,17,Ffurther north. Rain generally easing
OL,18,Fduring the early hours. Winds falling
OL,19,Flighter too. Very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
