OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday looks mostly cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some light drizzly rain on and
OL,7,Foff during the morning. Some heavier
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain are possible during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Breezy at times. Still
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOvernight rain gradually giving way to
OL,14,Fbrighter skies on Saturday with some
OL,15,Fsunshine. Turning damp and windy on
OL,16,FSunday. Further showery rain on
OL,17,FMonday, and still breezy. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
